Review Class

Cucumber is a framework/tool that supports BDD

Cucumber uses gherkin language
given - pre condition
when - action
then - result
and - continue any step
but

Feature high level feature/functionality of the system
Scenario

Background - common precondition steps inside 1 feature file can be defined using Background Keyword
Hooks - 2 hooks in cucumber (@Before, @After) - will run before and after every scenario from ALL feature files

cucumber supports DDT:

scenario outline - executes same sceanrio multiple times based on the data provided in Examples Table

cucumber datatable - execute same STEP multiples times based on data inside cucumber datatable

But if data becomes large --> we need to use Excel